title: [Orcswold, Village Camp]
description: The charred remains of an oft-used campfire fill a rough circle of stones in front of a low mud-roofed hut.  Scraps of bone and half-burnt animal skin litter the dirt near the firepit, and the overhanging branches of nearby trees are blackened with soot.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, southeast, west, northwest
